stories.summary: Australia should be removed from all official championships and only allowed to defend their World Cup title

stories.subTitle: New Zealand v Australia, 5th ODI, Napier

stories.title: Ponting delivers the whitewash

stories.summary: Australia sealed a 5-0 series victory over New Zealand with a massive 347 for 5 and a frightening early bowling display that earned them a 122-run win
